<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٨٧⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٢٥٩٣ - عَنْ عَلِيٍّ، عَنْ حَمَّادٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ إِبْرَاهِيمَ:</span> <span class="c2">«أَنَّهُ كَانَ يَسْتَعِيذُ بَعْدَ فَاتِحَةِ الْكِتَابِ»</span>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ حَمَّادٌ:</span> <span class="c2">«وَكَانَ سَعِيدُ بْنُ جُبَيْرٍ يَسْتَعِيذُ قَبْلَهَا»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>